# ClipSync 隐私政策 / Privacy Policy

最后更新日期 / Last Updated: 2024-06-25

---

## 简体中文

ClipSync（以下简称"本应用"）非常重视用户的隐私和数据安全。我们承诺严格保护您的个人信息，遵循相关法律法规。请您仔细阅读本隐私政策，了解我们的数据处理方式。

### 1. 数据收集与使用
- 本应用**不会收集、存储或上传**任何用户的剪贴板内容、个人信息或设备信息。
- 所有剪贴板数据仅在本地设备内存和本地数据库中处理，不会发送到任何服务器。

### 2. 数据存储与安全
- 剪贴板历史和收藏内容仅保存在您的本地设备上。
- 本应用不会将任何数据上传、同步或分享给第三方。
- 我们采用 macOS 沙盒机制，最大限度保障您的数据安全。

### 3. 第三方服务
- 本应用**不集成任何第三方 SDK、分析工具或广告服务**。

### 4. 用户权利
- 您可以随时通过应用内功能清除所有历史和收藏数据。
- 卸载应用后，所有本地数据将被彻底删除。

### 5. 政策变更
- 如本隐私政策有任何变更，我们将在应用更新日志或官方网站上公示。

### 6. 联系方式
如有任何隐私相关问题，请通过以下方式联系我们：
- 邮箱：fyddwwj@hotmail.com

---

## English

ClipSync ("the App") values your privacy and data security. We are committed to protecting your personal information in accordance with applicable laws and regulations. Please read this privacy policy carefully to understand how we handle your data.

### 1. Data Collection and Use
- The App **does not collect, store, or upload** any clipboard content, personal information, or device information.
- All clipboard data is processed only in your local device memory and local database, and is never sent to any server.

### 2. Data Storage and Security
- Clipboard history and favorites are stored only on your local device.
- The App does not upload, sync, or share any data with third parties.
- We use macOS sandboxing to maximize your data security.

### 3. Third-Party Services
- The App **does not integrate any third-party SDKs, analytics, or advertising services**.

### 4. User Rights
- You can clear all history and favorites at any time via the app's built-in features.
- All local data will be permanently deleted upon uninstallation.

### 5. Policy Changes
- If this privacy policy changes, we will announce it in the app update log or on the official website.

### 6. Contact
If you have any privacy-related questions, please contact us at:
- Email: fyddwwj@hotmail.com

---

> 本隐私政策适用于所有通过官方渠道（如 Mac App Store）下载和使用的 ClipSync 版本。
> This privacy policy applies to all versions of ClipSync downloaded and used via official channels (such as the Mac App Store). 
